    • Constructor Detail

      • TonPfxHashMap

        public TonPfxHashMap​(int keySize)
        HashMap with the fixed length keys. With comparison to TonHashMap, TonHashMapE may be empty. The first bit of it is a flag that indicates the emptiness. Notice, all keys should be of the same size. If you have keys of different size - align them. Duplicates are not allowed.
        Parameters:
        keySize - key size in bits
